title: In Nevada, days of counting votes lie ahead.
description: Final results are likely to take a week or so, with control of the U.S. Senate in the balance.
dc:creator: Danny Hakim, Jennifer Medina and Julie Brown

media:content.media:description: Joseph P. Gloria, the Clark County, Nev., registrar of voters, holding a news conference on Wednesday to discuss the process for getting election results.
